import pandas as pd

test = pd.read_csv('/Users/yenarue/OneDrive/Developer/Kaggle/titanic/test.csv')
train = pd.read_csv('/Users/yenarue/OneDrive/Developer/Kaggle/titanic/train.csv')

train["Child"] = 0;
train["Child"][train["Age"] < 18] = 1

print('아이들')
print(train["Survived"][train["Child"] == 1].value_counts(normalize = True))
print('성인')
print(train["Survived"][train["Child"] == 0].value_counts(normalize = True))
